---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 2026';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for United Hands Bangladesh. Please read these terms carefully before using our website and services.">
  <Header slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-cream)] to-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 text-[var(--color-primary)] text-sm font-medium px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
        Legal
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Last updated: {lastUpdated}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          By accessing or using the United Hands Bangladesh website (unitedhandsbd.org), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not access or use our website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">About United Hands Bangladesh</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          United Hands Bangladesh is a human rights organization dedicated to empowering communities through education, healthcare, community development, and humanitarian assistance. Our website provides information about our programs, allows for volunteer applications, and facilitates community engagement.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Use of Our Website</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Permitted Use</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You may use our website for lawful purposes, including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Learning about our organization and programs</li>
          <li>Contacting us for inquiries or support</li>
          <li>Subscribing to our newsletter</li>
          <li>Applying to volunteer</li>
          <li>Making donations through authorized channels</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Prohibited Use</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the website for any unlawful purpose</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
          <li>Transmit malware, viruses, or harmful code</li>
          <li>Collect personal information of other users without consent</li>
          <li>Impersonate our organization or staff members</li>
          <li>Use our content for commercial purposes without permission</li>
          <li>Engage in any activity that disrupts our website or services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          All content on this website, including text, images, logos, graphics, and design elements, is the property of United Hands Bangladesh or our content providers and is protected by copyright and intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">User-Submitted Content</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          When you submit information through our contact forms, volunteer applications, or other channels, you grant us permission to use this information to respond to your inquiry and for our legitimate organizational purposes. You represent that any information you provide is accurate and complete.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Donations</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Donations made to United Hands Bangladesh are voluntary and non-refundable unless otherwise agreed. All donations are used to support our charitable programs and operations. We provide acknowledgment of donations as required by applicable laws.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Volunteer Program</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Volunteer applications are subject to review and acceptance at our discretion. Volunteers must comply with our policies and guidelines. We reserve the right to terminate volunteer relationships at any time for any reason.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of service of external sites. Accessing third-party links is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our website and services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not guarantee that the website will be error-free, secure, or continuously available. We make reasonable efforts to ensure information accuracy but do not warrant completeness or reliability.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, United Hands Bangladesh shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our website or services. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount of any donation you have made to our organization in the past twelve months.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Indemnification</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless United Hands Bangladesh, its officers, staff, and volunteers from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from your violation of these Terms of Service or your use of our website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of Bangladesh. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Dhaka, Bangladesh.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          We may update these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective upon posting to this page. Your continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>United Hands Bangladesh</strong></p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-1">48 East Basabo, Dhaka-1214, Bangladesh</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-1">Email: support@unitedhandsbd.org</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Phone: +880 1825 554 945</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
